@startuml
[*] --> Order : new plane acquired
Order --> Arrival : delivered
Arrival --> Preparation
Preparation --> Operations : ready for operations
Preparation --> Maintenance : needs maintenance
Operations --> Operations : while flights scheduled
Operations --> Maintenance : no more flights or maintenance needed
Maintenance --> Preparation : servicing completed
Operations --> Withdrawn : withdrawn from service
Maintenance --> Withdrawn : withdrawn from service
Preparation --> Withdrawn : withdrawn during preparation
Arrival --> Withdrawn : withdrawn upon arrival
Order --> Withdrawn : withdrawn before delivery
Withdrawn --> [*]
@enduml
